Titolo: Fallout 1.5: Resurrection

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Fallout 1.5: Resurrection is a mod for Fallout 2. Developed by four fans of the game from the Czech Republic, a version was released there on 3 October 2013. Working on the mod during their free time, the development took approximately 10 years. The mod offers a completely new story and locations. It is estimated that finishing the game takes 25 hours.The title Resurrection symbolizes not only a revival of an old Fallout but also the protagonist of the mod who is resurrected.The English version of the mod was released on 15 July 2016.

Genere: Role-playing 

Valutazione: N/A
